  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BackEndDataProvider<VaadinSession,Predicate<? super VaadinSession>>, DataProvider<VaadinSession,Predicate<? super VaadinSession>>, Serializable

    public class VaadinSessionDataProvider
extends CallbackDataProvider<VaadinSession,Predicate<? super VaadinSession>>
    A DataProvider that contains all live VaadinSessions.

    The sessions are retrieved from the SimpleSpringServlet, which must be configured with session tracking enabled.

    See Also:
    SimpleSpringServlet, Serialized Form
